ation officials</strong> told me they are fighting back against the Chinese government&rsquo;s campaign for more important reasons than just making China look bad.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;The reason China&rsquo;s actions are dangerous is because their censorship supercharged a virus that has now turned into a global pandemic,&rdquo; a senior administration official told me. &ldquo;By ignoring their responsibility and deflecting attention away from the core problem &mdash; their misgovernance &mdash; <strong>they are avoiding the transparency that ultimately keeps their people, and us, safe</strong>.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nFailing to call out this behavior now, the official said, could come back to haunt the world in the future. &ldquo;If they don&rsquo;t change their behavior now and admit their actions had consequences, there&rsquo;s every reason to expect similar results the next time a virus erupts in China,&rdquo; the official said."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T15:45:32.000Z","msg":"Well said"},{"pid":"ebd50aedee5ce1a0e8fcb60540ffcc99a8c100f0","tid":1932160,"uid":63934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T15:46:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/93/Titan_II_launch.jpg/1200px-Titan_II_launch.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F9%2F93%2FTitan_II_launch.jpg%2F1200px-Titan_II_launch.jpg&h=5139337f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n直接射落中國算了吧"},{"pid":"215969bc78121ff36acf919a4321c5bf18779483","tid":1932160,"uid":41545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6b1835316eecc7d514b5126dc6783d91c7cc7ec","tid":1932160,"uid":63154,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T15:32:23.000Z","msg":"都話賴美國係一大錯誤，小學生做國家主席真係加速將中國帶入一條死路"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T15:49:12.000Z","msg":"某程度上做得好呀維尼<br />\n唔咁煽風點火點做到咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi