tting-lives-risk/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Trump administration officials</strong> told me they are fighting back against the Chinese government&rsquo;s campaign for more important reasons than just making China look bad.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;The reason China&rsquo;s actions are dangerous is because their censorship supercharged a virus that has now turned into a global pandemic,&rdquo; a senior administration official told me. &ldquo;By ignoring their responsibility and deflecting attention away from the core problem &mdash; their misgovernance &mdash; <strong>they are avoiding the transparency that ultimately keeps their people, and us, safe</strong>.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nFailing to call out this behavior now, the official said, could come back to haunt the world in the future. &ldquo;If they don&rsquo;t change their behavior now and admit their actions had consequences, there&rsquo;s every reason to expect similar results the next time a virus erupts in China,&rdquo; the official said."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T17:07:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"702b60943787c5fca7cab1b33898aa9a2e007d4a","tid":1932160,"uid":35507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T17:07:43.000Z","msg":"清算支共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b81601e0ba8d95fee2ed5f5abc63da8d4b5919e","tid":1932160,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T17:13:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f0e753e68759d57afb901dbb3b37f0a5ac1c8652","tid":1932160,"uid":139294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T17:16:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"74518436814b3b765471b8c20e1927e0aa188ab7","tid":1932160,"uid":218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T17:16:37.000Z","msg":"幾時清走美國嘅小粉紅"},{"pid":"53fc596bcd6ba027a5613d8773076ff3f12c784a","tid":1932160,"uid":301139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"47b66be357aaa67d539686788ab7def70087a631","tid":19